Class StudentList

java.lang.Object
StudentList
public class StudentList
extends java.lang.Object
This class makes a list of Students. The methods are used to add to, remove from or print from the current set of Students.
Author:
Chris Zachariah (cvz2), Anthony Topol (at877)
